            "bgImage": "shopify://shop_images/Web_1920_2_43d730f7-eef7-4bc1-be5a-e85fa1201936.jpg",
            "heading": "Geranium & Ylang Ylang",
            "detail": "A scented blend of enchanting floral gardens and warm, spicy tropics.   Tap to Discover More >",
            "pop_heading": "Geranium & Ylang Ylang",
            "pop_detail": "<p>Top Notes: </p> <p>Ylang Ylang - a deep, rich floral aroma that's slightly sweet and promotes relaxation, kills bacteria and lowers blood pressure.</p> <p>Geranium - Intensely floral, sweet and rosy oil that supports emotions by creating a calming and grounding effect. </p> <p>Base Notes: </p> <p>Coriander - an invigorating, stimulating oil with a powerful, sweet, somewhat spicy and warm aroma, with a lively woody/peppery top note and a balsamic undertone. </p> <p>Clary Sage - Clary sage smells sweet and herbaceous with ambery tones of fresh tobacco. The oil promotes inner tranquillity and dispels negativity. </p> <p>Ho Wood - Sweet and floral, Ho Wood essential oil promotes peace and tranquillity. </p>",
            "showplus": true,
            "PoopupIconCode": "<div>\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Ylang-scent.png?v=1683634425\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Ho_wood-scent.png?v=1683634425\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Sage-scent.png?v=1683634425\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/geranium-scent.png?v=1683634425\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Coriander-scent.png?v=1683634425\">\n        </div>\n<div></div>"
          }
